trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry" />.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta clase no puede heredarse.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry> objects specify access rights for specific key containers.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry> los objetos especifican los derechos de acceso para determinados contenedores de claves.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry" /> object to add.
